FBIS4-58363 "drnes086_j_94009" FBIS-NES-94-086 Daily Report 3 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen MBC Reports Troop Movements in South Yemen MBC Reports Troop Movements in South Yemen NC0305185794 London MBC Television in Arabic 1800 GMT 3 May 94 NC0305185794 London MBC Television Arabic BFN [Text] A military spokesman in Aden today accused northern armored forces of encircling a southern brigade and of taking up fighting positions in an area adjacent to the southern 1st Brigade in Yarim. The southern Yemeni spokesman warned of the consequences of involving the country in a destructive civil war, particularly after last week's clashes between southern and northern military units in the 'Imran area which left more than 200 soldiers killed or wounded and caused heavy losses of equipment.
